Scala game needs
    - hero
    - weapon
    - choice options
    - database to store something
    - should be able to store what happens in game into external text file
    -  must be able to update the hero with new weapons etc..


    - Your application must be able to and store the data contained within those files in a database
    - Your application should be able to have basic CRUD functionalities
    - Your application should have a CLI where users can interact with the application while it is running
    - Your application should be able to log all activities during runtime and store logs into an external text file


    
    
    
    
    
    